# ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

AI Content Generator is a dynamic web-based application designed to generate **high-quality written content** using **Large Language Models (LLMs)**.

Built with **Streamlit** and powered by **Meta LLaMA 3 (8B Instruct)** via the **Hugging Face API**, the application enables users to create:

- Professional Emails  
- LinkedIn Posts  
- Advertisements  
- Conversational Content  

Users can customize tone, language, and writing style while maintaining a seamless and interactive experience.

The platform integrates secure authentication, personalized history tracking, theme customization, and a modern dashboard interface.

