# ğŸ¯ Summary

AI Content Generator is a full-stack AI-powered web application that combines:

- Secure user authentication  
- Advanced LLM-based content generation  
- Theme customization  
- Structured history management  
- Modern UI design  

The project demonstrates practical implementation of **LLM integration, authentication systems, session management, user personalization, and content storage architecture** in a real-world application.
